(36381, 114690, 3479, 2, 'Little Marriage', '', '2011-06-01 00:00:00', 2010, 30, 0, 7, '', 'A year and a day could pass just as quickly\nAnd I don''t mind, I don''t mind\nIf they end as they should be\n\nYour open eyes are two private oceans\nThey don''t cry, I don''t mind \nTo see your devotion\n\nLittle Marriage blew through this home\nWith a difference between us and have & hold\nWhat is this marrow we''re burrowed upon,\nWhen your face is the answer and the question''s this song?\n\nI got caught on a day thrill,\nCan''t see you tonight,\nI don''t mind but you do?\nI don''t mind what you say\nIf you don''t mind where I''m going\nDevotion is known and not for showing\n\nSomething smaller keeps us in tow\nWith a difference between us and have & hold\nI started minding not having it all\nOne little marriage or big love', 189, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-06-16 15:11:57', '2015-03-12 13:47:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(36382, 114690, 3479, 3, 'Bag Of Wind', '', '2011-06-01 00:00:00', 2010, 30, 0, 7, '', 'Leave the light\nLet the candle glow\nBreathe deep, slower\nIn this storm\nIf I had just\nStayed in Mexico\nWhere I am full\nAnd the weather suits by clothes\n\nWe breathe a life\nAccepting this big home\nWhen we are forever warm\n\nWell, if I''m not here\nAnd I have delayed\nPlease say\nI''ve gone away along\nBut I have had\nMy own bag of wind at the shore\nAnd the sun works hard\nTo make all live long\n\nWell, if I were here\nGentle me in complete\nHolding me around\nThen go to naturally\nWhile flowers weep\nGentle me in complete\nHolding me around\nThen go to naturally\n\n', 245, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-06-16 15:16:04', '2015-03-12 13:47:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(36383, 114690, 3479, 4, 'After Is Always Before', '', '2011-06-01 00:00:00', 2010, 30, 0, 7, '', '\nGetting high, you could never stay behind\nHowever known you are is a choice you''ll find\nBut won''t you stay nice?\n\nGetting by I was only saying\nWould you really die before you lost your meaning?\nBut won''t you stay nice?\n\nI say you''re golden babe, and I sing for your song\nI don''t know after and before''s almost gone\nWhen everybody learned where you would''ve gone\nI said that''s where he''s going and it''s not everyone\n\nYou said so much and now I realize it more\nWherever we go, after is always before\nAnd won''t you stay nice?\n\nI say you''re golden babe and I''ll sing for your song\nI don''t know after and before''s almost gone\nGo go the teller''s been waiting outside\nHe''s been waiting for days\nFor yesterday''s night\n', 259, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2011-06-16 15:24:22', '2015-03-12 13:47:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
