(36394, 107522, 0, 1, 'Dirty Little Sky (Demo)', '髒小天', '2011-06-16 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '　\r\n嘗試著訴說某些想法和理念\r\n\r\n他們卻說這不過是偷梗系列\r\n\r\n而當重新排列組合被我發現\r\n\r\n他們則否決　好將所有威脅都消滅\r\n\r\n\r\n沒什麼　好說明\r\n\r\n沒地位的　小人物　似乎是　一個原因\r\n\r\n沒什麼　好可惜\r\n\r\n就是　酸葡萄心理　見縫插針的　邏輯\r\n\r\n\r\nStand in the mainstream　是否能　從這鬼地方逃離出去\r\n\r\nStand in the mainstream　催眠般　無止盡洗腦人們心靈\r\n\r\nStand in the mainstream　他們說　只有這扇門才是真理\r\n\r\nWell, give an applause to the funny definition\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n咖啡泡麵哥戴著帥氣墨鏡\r\n\r\n標竿哥依舊高在空中盤據\r\n\r\n約翰尼乘坐著潮男熱氣球\r\n\r\n用盡所有手段　也要把你打下天空\r\n\r\n\r\n沒什麼　好說明\r\n\r\n說的也　不過是只有　大人物　才可以\r\n\r\n沒什麼　好可惜\r\n\r\n他們只關心　自己　受損的　既得利益\r\n\r\n\r\nStand in the mainstream　是否能　從這鬼地方逃離出去\r\n\r\nStand in the mainstream　催眠般　無止盡洗腦人們心靈\r\n\r\nStand in the mainstream　他們說　只有這扇門才是真理\r\n\r\nWell, give an applause to the funny definition\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nYou may say : I walk this lonely way\r\n\r\nI would say : Face yourself with trueness\r\n\r\nYou may say : I walk this lonely way\r\n\r\nI must say : Face myself with honesty\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe''re standing in this fucking mainstream\r\n\r\nWe''re standing in this fucking mainstream\r\n\r\nWe''re living in this fucking mainstream\r\n\r\nWe''re stucking in this fucking mainstream\r\n　\r\n　', '', 299, '', 'Black Friday', '黑色星期五', '黑の金曜日', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-06-16 22:54:22', '2015-03-12 13:47:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
